flowRoot.flowPara: It's an infinite space where items can be placed and connected together.
Hold shift and click here to create a node.
shift click here again to create another node.
Hold down the right mouse button down on this node, and start dragging right
As you continue to hold the right mouse button, pass the cursor over this node.
Release the right mouse button over this node.
This is a link. It connects the from the first node, via the second node, to the last node.
